data.description: **Discover Your Ideal Retreat!** This charming ranch-style home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 672-square-foot cellar-style basement on a sprawling 1.28-acre lot. Enjoy the best of both worlds with a country feel just 5 minutes from town. The open living spaces, abundant natural light, and private well add to the appeal. Step outside to a vast yard, perfect for outdoor activities and gardening. Embrace the tranquility of rural living while maintaining easy access to local amenities and commuting routes. Don't miss this opportunity to make this countryside gem your own. Contact Cathy (307) 851-1880 or Spencer (307) 851-6885 at Home Source Realty for more details.
